Filter Your Data
Apply global filters in a dashboard to focus on the subset of data that’s most relevant for your business unit, project, or management team.

Tap  to open the Global Filters panel.
Tap a filter to open the filter configuration panel.
Change the filter settings, and tap Done.
The visualizations in your dashboard change to show the data through the filter you created.
